\id 3JN - SYN-Siyin Bible 
\h 3 JOHN 
\toc1 3 JOHN 
\toc2 3 John 
\toc3 3Jn 
\mt1 JOHN  
\mt3 Laithak Thumna  
\mt2 Third John  
\c 1  
\s1 Paupuina  
\p
\v 1 Upa pa in ka it mama Gaias, thutak sungah kong it:   
\p
\v 2 Ka it lawm awng, thin le lung na picin bangma in, na theampo ah na picin tu le na dam tu kong deisak hi.   
\s1 Lungdamna Lianbel  
\p
\v 3 Nangma sia thutak sungah na nuntak bangma in, na sungah om thutak sia, suapui te hongpai in hong son uh ciang nasiatak in ka lungdam hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ka tate thutak sungah nungta hi, ci thu ka zak ciang sang in, a lianzaw lungdamna nei ngawl khi hi.   
\s1 Gaias  
\p
\v 5 Ka it ka lawm awng, suapui te le leangna te tungah na vawt theampo thumantak in na vawt hi;   
\p
\v 6 Amate in na itna thu pawlpi mai ah son uh hi; nangma in amate khualhawna mun ah Pathian deina bang in na tha le, napha seam seam na hihi:   
\p
\v 7 Banghangziam cile amate sia Ama min hang in Gentile te kung pan bangma la ngawl in pai hi.   
\p
\v 8 Tua ahikom eite thutak dinpui tu te i hi thei natu in tabang te i san tu a hihi.   
\s1 Diotrephes  
\p
\v 9 Pawlpi tungah lai ka thak hi: ahihang amate sungah lampui a suaknuam Diotrephes in hong sang nuam ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 10 Tua ahikom kongpai a a hile ama hong vawt nate mangil ngawl tu khi hi, ama in kamsia taw hong selno hi: tuabek taw lungkim ngawl lai in suapui te sang nuam ngawl a, a sang nuam te zong khak in pawlpi sung pan hawlkhia hi.   
\p
\v 11 Ka it ka lawm awng, a phangawlte zui heak in, ahizong a pha te zui in. Na pha a seam te Pathian neisa a hihi: ahihang na phangawl a seam te in Pathian mu ngawl lai hi.   
\s1 Demetrius  
\p
\v 12 Mi theampo sia Demetrius i tetti hi, thutak cikteak ama i tetti a hihi: kote zong ama sang pan tetti ka hi uh hi; kong son te maan hi, ci na he uh hi.   
\s1 A Khakbel Nuksetna  
\p
\v 13 No tungah at tu tam mama nei khi hi, hikale laikung le laitui taw at ngawl tu khi hi.   
\p
\v 14 Ahihang hai ngawl in hong mu tu in ki um khi hi, maitang kisi in i ki paupui tu hi.   
\p
\v 15 Thinnopna hong om tahen. I lawm te in hong nukset hi. Lawmte minlo in nukset in.   